entries.femaleVariant: That uh... That delivery ever come? The meds?
Yeah, came in, but more of the same shit. Nobody's touchin' it.
'Ey... Y'ask me, they couldn't sell it in town, thought they'd push the scop on us.
Best part is, someone at the top thought vitamins would sell in that shithole.
Hahaha! An' then they're scratchin' their heads, wonderin' why everyone's down at the market.
Yeah, well, we need real meds, not some Leelou Beans with niacin or whatever the fuck.
But real meds cost real scratch. That's somethin' we ain't got.
